value: Breeds on the inland lakes of the high plateaus of central Asia from Chinese Turkestan to southern Mongolia and south to Ladak and the eastern Himalayas. Winters on the coasts of southern Asia from the Gulf of Aden to Tenasserim and in the Gulf of Siam.
